# Block all .env.* by default, then re-include the two files that need
# to ship with the image. `.env.example` is documentation; `.env.dev` is
# the baseline config for the dev ECS task (ECS env vars + secrets layer
# on top of it at task start).
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.dev
